36:24.030 --> 36:26.830
JORDAN:
Hello, Ackley!

36:27.400 --> 36:30.030
Hello, Ackley!

36:30.030 --> 36:32.570
What do we all think of
Ackley Bridge College, then?

36:32.570 --> 36:34.170
