37:25.170 --> 37:26.000
Nasreen!

37:29.830 --> 37:31.670
What, you just going to
stand there and not say owt?

37:31.670 --> 37:33.900
-Missy, I´m sorry.
-You what?

37:33.900 --> 37:35.830
