every name going.

37:35.830 --> 37:38.970
Slag. Nasty. Junkie.
My mum?

37:38.970 --> 37:40.170
Treated her like she was scum.

37:40.170 --> 37:41.630
Go on, Missy, smack her!

37:41.630 --> 37:44.830
