think of you.

37:47.570 --> 37:48.970
Look, Missy, they´re me mates.

37:48.970 --> 37:51.830
You don´t know them,
like I don´t know your mates.

37:51.830 --> 37:53.830
It´s not my fault that you
got held back a year, is it?

37:53.830 --> 37:55.830
[ All groaning ]

37:56.870 --> 37:58.300
Missy, what are you doing?

37:58.300 --> 38:00.570
Oh, like you don´t know
how to fight back?

38:00.570 --> 38:02.970
Oh, oh,
´cause you´re so perfect!

38:02.970 --> 38:03.930
You´re so good!

38:03.930 --> 38:05.070
You´re such a good
little Muslim,

38:05.070 --> 38:06.870
you fit right in with that lot.

38:06.870 --> 38:10.270
You were out drinking with me
in town not two nights ago.

38:10.270 --> 38:13.000
With the kutti.
With the gori.

38:13.000 --> 38:15.700
Ohh!
Oh, the shame!

38:15.700 --> 38:16.700
[ Screams ]

38:16.700 --> 38:18.830
[ All shouting ]

38:18.830 --> 38:21.030
[ Chanting "Fight, fight!" ]

38:24.570 --> 38:26.230
Yeah, come on, Missy!

38:26.230 --> 38:28.370
