38:28.370 --> 38:30.900
[ Chanting continues ]

38:37.970 --> 38:39.200
Stop!

38:40.030 --> 38:41.200
Stop!

38:41.200 --> 38:43.100
Stop!
Out the way!

38:43.100 --> 38:45.630
Stop, Missy!
Missy, get off her, get off her.

38:45.630 --> 38:47.570
-Get off her!
-HAYLEY: Oh, my God, Miss.

38:47.570 --> 38:49.900
-What you gonna do?
-You all right?

38:49.900 --> 38:50.830
Yeah?

38:50.830 --> 38:52.570
Move. Everyone.
Out of it!

38:52.570 --> 38:54.370
-You okay?
-Yeah, thanks for your help!

38:54.370 --> 38:56.570
What, you expect me to hit her
or summat?

38:57.830 --> 39:00.630
EMMA: What are you doing?
She´s your best mate, ain´t she?

39:00.630 --> 39:02.030
