39:02.900 --> 39:04.430
You don´t attack her
in the quad.

39:04.430 --> 39:06.000
-Sorry, Miss, about --
-Calm yourself down.

39:06.000 --> 39:07.570
Calm yourself down.

39:07.570 --> 39:09.070
-Can I go home, Miss?
-Missy.

39:09.070 --> 39:09.970
Please, Miss.

39:09.970 --> 39:12.030
EMMA: Missy, don´t fight
with your friends.

39:12.030 --> 39:13.830
You don´t get many
good ones in life.

39:13.830 --> 39:15.400
Go on, take her home.
Go on.

39:26.700 --> 39:28.270
I see. Yes.

39:28.270 --> 39:30.070
