then?"

39:45.600 --> 39:46.670
"No, don´t do that."

39:46.670 --> 39:49.830
It´s just this school
is just not what I expected!

39:49.830 --> 39:51.500
And it´s not fair!
It´s not fair on me.

39:51.500 --> 39:53.630
But no one´s thinking
about that, are they? No!

39:53.630 --> 39:54.600
Well, life isn´t fair.

39:54.600 --> 39:57.030
But in this house, we don´t
feel sorry for ourselves!

39:57.030 --> 39:59.430
And I don´t want the teacher
phoning me again.

39:59.430 --> 40:00.970
[ Groans ]

40:03.070 --> 40:04.670
I am not having that boy
ruin this place

40:04.670 --> 40:06.430
before we´ve even got going.

40:06.430 --> 40:07.970
