whether I´m sleeping with Sadiq?

40:21.500 --> 40:23.070
[ Door opens ]

40:25.600 --> 40:26.900
[ Door closes ]

40:30.170 --> 40:31.830
Why it is important

40:31.830 --> 40:35.200
to respect other people´s
beliefs and cultures?

40:35.200 --> 40:36.500
